Digunakan untuk **halaman detail/review KRS** (`/adminpage/approvalKRS/{id}`).

**Path Params**:
| Param     | Type    | Required | Keterangan        |
|-----------|---------|----------|-------------------|
| studentId | integer | required | User ID mahasiswa |

**Query Params**:
