|---------------------|---------|----------|------------------------------------------------------|
| id_academic_period  | integer | optional | Filter per periode (default: periode aktif)          |

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Data KRS mahasiswa berhasil diambil.",
  "data": {
