### A5. PATCH /api/manager/krs/{id}/reject
**Deskripsi**: Tolak pengajuan KRS dengan alasan (hanya status `pending`).

**Path Params**:
| Param | Type    | Required | Keterangan |
|-------|---------|----------|------------|
| id    | integer | required | KRS ID     |

**Request Body**:
```json
{ "rejection_reason": "Kelas sudah penuh. Silakan pilih kelas lain dengan subject yang sama." }
```

| Field            | Type   | Required | Keterangan                          |
|------------------|--------|----------|-------------------------------------|
| rejection_reason | string | required | Alasan penolakan, minimal 10 karakter, maksimal 500 karakter |

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "KRS mahasiswa berhasil ditolak.",
  "data": {
    "id_krs": 1,
    "status": "rejected",
    "processed_by": 5,
    "processed_at": "2026-05-16T15:30:00.000000Z",
    "rejection_reason": "Kelas sudah penuh. Silakan pilih kelas lain dengan subject yang sama.",
    "student": { "id_user_si": 100, "name": "Wachyoudi", "username": "wachyoudi123" },
    "subject": { "id_subject": 1, "name_subject": "Basis Data", "code_subject": "SVPL1234", "sks": 2 },
    "krsClass": { "id_class": 10, "code_class": "A" },
    "academicPeriod": { "id_academic_period": 1, "name": "Semester Ganjil 2024/2025" },
    "processor": { "id_user_si": 5, "name": "Current Manager" }
  }
}
```

**Response Error (422)**:
```json
{ "status": "error", "message": "Hanya pengajuan KRS yang berstatus pending yang dapat ditolak." }
```
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": null,
  "errors": {
    "rejection_reason": ["Alasan penolakan wajib diisi.", "Alasan penolakan minimal 10 karakter."]
  }
}
```

