| id    | integer | required | KRS session ID |

**Request Body**: kosong / tidak diperlukan

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Sesi KRS berhasil ditutup.",
  "data": {
    "id_krs_session": 1,
    "id_academic_period": 1,
    "status": "closed",
    "opened_at": "2026-05-01T09:00:00.000000Z",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-30T17:00:00.000000Z",
    "academic_period": { "id_academic_period": 1, "name": "Semester Ganjil 2024/2025" },
    "opener": { "id_user_si": 5, "name": "Manager User" },
