### B5. GET /api/manager/krs-sessions/{id}/classes
**Deskripsi**: Daftar kelas yang terdaftar dalam sesi KRS tertentu (dengan pagination).

**Path Params**:
| Param | Type    | Required | Keterangan     |
|-------|---------|----------|----------------|
| id    | integer | required | KRS session ID |

**Query Params**:
| Param      | Type    | Required | Keterangan                  |
|------------|---------|----------|-----------------------------|
| id_subject | integer | optional | Filter per mata kuliah      |
| search     | string  | optional | Cari nama/kode mata kuliah  |
| per_page   | integer | optional | Default: 20                 |
| page       | integer | optional | Default: 1                  |

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Daftar kelas sesi KRS berhasil diambil.",
  "data": {
    "session": {
      "id_krs_session": 1,
      "status": "open",
      "id_academic_period": 1
    },
    "classes": {
      "current_page": 1,
      "data": [
        {
          "id_krs_session_class": 1,
          "id_krs_session": 1,
          "id_subject": 1,
          "id_class": 10,
          "subject": { "id_subject": 1, "name_subject": "Basis Data", "code_subject": "SVPL1234", "sks": 2 },
          "krsClass": {
            "id_class": 10,
            "code_class": "A",
            "day_of_week": "Senin",
            "start_time": "08:00:00",
            "end_time": "10:30:00",
