| CRUD /manager/subjects                      | ✅    | ✅      |
| CRUD /manager/classes                       | ✅    | ✅      |
| GET  /academic-periods                      | ✅    | ✅      |
| POST/PUT/DELETE /academic-periods           | ✅    | ✅      |
| GET/POST/DELETE /admin/managers             | ✅    | ❌      |

